Package: wickraimpact
Type: Package
Title: Market-Impact Backtesting on the Real Historical Order Book
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-impact over its C ABI hub: replace the fill
    stage of a backtest with an order-book walk on the real historical L2 book,
    so slippage is measured, not guessed - byte-identical to the CLI and every
    other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-impact
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-impact/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-impact C ABI shared library (WKIMPACT_LIB)
    and its header (WKIMPACT_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
